Package: DTANetPerturbeR
Title: Drug-Target binding Affinity based Network Perturbation approach for drug Repurposing
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Yitan", 
           family = "Lu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "yitanlu02@gmail.com")
Description: 
    This package is used for drug repurposing based on binding affinity weighted
    drug-target-gene network perturbation analysis.
    It includes three main steps: constructing the disease network, 
    identifying the target module, and drug repurposing.
